This update marks the beginning of the [[Spring 2015 Event]]. 
* The event is presumably based upon Operation 11.
* One of the event prizes will be a Battleship from the [[wikipedia:Littorio-class battleship|Littorio class]]. Other new ships are also expected to appear in the event.
* The event will last approximately 20 days. 
* Aircraft carriers (CVs) will play a heavy role during this event.

This page merely lines out the basic information for this update. For information on the actual event, please visit [[Spring 2015 Event|this page]].

